data.description: MOVE IN READY !!! The open floor plan farm house on a dead end street has great views and sunsets. The Kitchen has been completely redone including new appliances , cabinets, countertops and a farm house sink. Both bathrooms have been remodeled as well .The beautiful tilework in them is  a must see.  There are two additional bonus areas have heat, and are ready for your office, guest bedrooms or additional living space. The possibilities are endless !!! Nearly new, water heater, furnace, central AC and upgraded 220 AMP electric. New Garage doors with an opener and keypad. Newer laminate flooring through out main living areas.   Call for your appointment today!!!
